718
00:37:54,599 --> 00:37:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] I to sam doživio u sjemeništu.

719
00:37:56,980 --> 00:37:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] I to doživljavam danas na župi

720
00:37:58,440 --> 00:37:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] na jedan drugi način,

721
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] i kao povjerenik za pastoral mladih.

722
00:38:01,380 --> 00:38:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna stvar koja me fascinira,

723
00:38:03,539 --> 00:38:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] što vidim obraćenja.

724
00:38:05,079 --> 00:38:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidiš da Isus i danas,

725
00:38:07,780 --> 00:38:10,559
[SPEAKER_00] ona je bio nekakva lopina do sad,

726
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam, nešto se u njemu vrtilo,

727
00:38:13,940 --> 00:38:15,380
[SPEAKER_00] bio je sasvim daleko,

728
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] a sad odjednom dolazi redovito

729
00:38:18,199 --> 00:38:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] na svetu misu,

730
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi na svetu ispovjed,

731
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:23,800
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi kako je Bog velik.

732
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što mene kao svećenika ispunja.

733
00:38:27,099 --> 00:38:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ne znam koliko sam vam pomogao

734
00:38:30,039 --> 00:38:32,480
[SPEAKER_00] s ovom pričom, svojom životnom,

735
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:35,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je ono kako sam ja doživio gospodina.

736
00:38:35,019 --> 00:38:36,900
[SPEAKER_00] I rekao bih jednu stvar,

737
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:39,360
[SPEAKER_00] u životu ništa ne bih mijenjao.

738
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što sam vidio da je moj križ

739
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:44,019
[SPEAKER_00] bio moj blagoslov.

740
00:38:44,019 --> 00:38:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] I da rane ono što su me drugi ranili,

741
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] što su tebe ranili,

742
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] trebaju postati naši biseri.

743
00:38:50,199 --> 00:38:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] Naši biseri.

744
00:38:52,159 --> 00:38:53,900
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako ne bi postali biseri,

745
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi mi ranjavali druge.

746
00:38:55,239 --> 00:38:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] To ne bi bilo dobro.

747
00:38:57,099 --> 00:38:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] I dolaze mi u pamet riječi,

748
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] evo za vas,

749
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji se ovdje okupljate u Botinicu,

750
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] jedna nova zajednica,

751
00:39:03,699 --> 00:39:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] nešto prekrasno,

752
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] što duh poručuje crkvi,

753
00:39:07,820 --> 00:39:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] našoj crkvi u Hrvata.

754
00:39:09,340 --> 00:39:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] Poslužio bih sednom rečenicom

755
00:39:12,679 --> 00:39:14,219
[SPEAKER_00] Svetog pape Ivana Paola II.

756
00:39:15,039 --> 00:39:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ako budete ono što biste trebali biti,

757
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:21,079
[SPEAKER_00] vi ćete zapaliti cijeli Botinec.

758
00:39:21,079 --> 00:39:22,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo Botinec.

759
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:35,280
[SPEAKER_00] nego i Zagrebi,

760
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,260
[SPEAKER_00] našu domovinu.

761
00:39:36,260 --> 00:39:37,260
[SPEAKER_00] Isus se posluže

762
00:39:37,260 --> 00:39:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] s 12 apostola,

763
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji su bili puni duha.

764
00:39:39,559 --> 00:39:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] Evo to želim i molim vama,

765
00:39:41,239 --> 00:39:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] da sve ove naše životne priče,

766
00:39:43,460 --> 00:39:44,679
[SPEAKER_00] sve što nam se događa,

767
00:39:44,679 --> 00:39:45,860
[SPEAKER_00] bude u toj službi,

768
00:39:45,860 --> 00:39:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] da osjetimo da bez gospodina ne možemo.

769
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:50,019
[SPEAKER_00] I najvažnija meni,

770
00:39:50,019 --> 00:39:51,860
[SPEAKER_00] jedna od najljepših rečenica,

771
00:39:51,860 --> 00:39:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] koje sam čuo,

772
00:39:52,679 --> 00:39:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira što vam se u životu dogodilo,

773
00:39:55,719 --> 00:39:58,719
[SPEAKER_00] postoji samo jedna tragedija u životu,

774
00:39:58,719 --> 00:40:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] a ta je da ne budete sveti.

775
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] Budite sveti, budite Boži.

